OL,3,CHomeowners hit with huge fees after
OL,4,Claw firm collapse appeal for
OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,FHomeowners in Bradford say they risk
OL,8,Flosing their homes and their health
OL,9,Fafter the no-win no-fee law firm
OL,10,Frepresenting them went bust.
OL,12,FThey are among an estimated 10,000
OL,13,Fpeople nationwide who were offered
OL,14,Ffree legal representation by SSB law
OL,15,Fto pursue compensation claims for
OL,16,Finsulation that they say caused damp
OL,17,Fand mould in their homes.
OL,19,FAfter SSB went into administration in
OL,20,FJanuary, some have been hit by eye-
OL,21,Fwatering legal fees.
