OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,FSince the insulation was originally
OL,8,Finstalled as part of a free Government
OL,9,Fscheme, they are now calling on
OL,10,Fministers to compensate them.
OL,12,FAilsa White had the cavity wall
OL,13,Finsulation installed in 2017.
OL,15,FSince then, for the past seven years,
OL,16,Fshe says damp and mould has destroyed
OL,17,Fher home.
