OL,3,CHomeowners hit with huge fees after
OL,4,Claw firm collapse appeal for
OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,F"I was disgusted," Ailsa said. "The
OL,8,Fmould was everywhere - and it was
OL,9,Fpeach, orange, grey, black. It was
OL,10,Fdisgusting."
OL,12,FSSB Law approached Ailsa, telling her
OL,13,Fshe could fight back with a 'no-win no-
OL,14,Ffee claim', but this year, the law
OL,15,Ffirm collapsed, and she was told the
OL,16,Fcosts would be handed to her.
OL,18,FAilsa says the stress and strain of
OL,19,Fdealing with SSB Law have made her ill.
