OL,4,Claw firm collapse appeal for
OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,F"I collapsed in my own kitchen - I
OL,8,Fbanged my head, lost consciousness and
OL,9,Fended up with a concussion. I had to
OL,10,Fgo to hospital and was put under a
OL,11,Fcardiologist and the faint clinic. I
OL,12,Fhad all sorts of investigations - and
OL,13,Fit was just stress."
OL,15,FAilsa hasn't been told exactly how
OL,16,Fmuch she'll have to repay - but
OL,17,Fbelieves it could be between #40,000
OL,18,Fand #50,000, on top of the ongoing
OL,19,Fcosts of the defective insulation.
