OL,3,CHomeowners hit with huge fees after
OL,4,Claw firm collapse appeal for
OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,FAn online group, set up to support
OL,8,Fothers who have been hit by bills
OL,9,Fafter SSB's collapse, estimates that
OL,10,Fup to 10,000 people could be in the
OL,11,Fsame position.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, some of them took their
OL,14,Fprotest to Parliament, calling on the
OL,15,FGovernment to compensate them.
OL,17,FQurrah Ahmed, from Bradford, attended
OL,18,Fthe protest on behalf of her father,
OL,19,Fwho borrowed money to repay his claim.
