OL,4,Claw firm collapse appeal for
OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,FQurrah said, "he was living in
OL,8,Fabsolute fear. He's got high blood
OL,9,Fpressure, he's got health issues and
OL,10,Fhe's also in his seventies, so he's an
OL,11,Fold vulnerable person."
OL,13,FHer MP, Imran Hussain, along with
OL,14,FBradford South MP Judith Cummins,
OL,15,FBarry Sheerman MP and Holly Lynch MP,
OL,16,Fheld a meeting to share similar
OL,17,Fstories from their constituents.
