OL,3,CHomeowners hit with huge fees after
OL,4,Claw firm collapse appeal for
OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,FMr Hussain, who represents the
OL,8,FBradford East constituency, said: "I
OL,9,Fhad a case of a pensioner served with
OL,10,Fa notice of #11,000 days before
OL,11,FChristmas - can you imagine what went
OL,12,Fthrough his mind, someone living on
OL,13,Fvery limited means? And we also have
OL,14,Fthe cost of living crisis, many people
OL,15,Fup and down the country are on the
OL,16,Fpoverty line."
OL,18,FMr Hussain is joining other MPs to
OL,19,Fcall on the Government to provide
OL,20,Fcompensation for victims.
