OL,4,Claw firm collapse appeal for
OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,FA Government spokesperson said "The UK
OL,8,Fhas one of the strongest consumer
OL,9,Fprotection regimes in the world
OL,10,Fincluding serious penalties for those
OL,11,Fwho fail to comply."
OL,13,FIn the House of Commons on Wednesday,
OL,14,FJustice Secretary Alex Chalk also
OL,15,Fpromised to look into the issue.
OL,17,FBut not everyone hit by huge bills
OL,18,Fsays the Government is to blame.
OL,26,@oD@`OUsD@TO]
