OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,FWhile some, like Ailsa, believe the
OL,8,FGovernment's insulation scheme ruined
OL,9,Ftheir homes, others say SSB convinced
OL,10,Fthem to take out claims, even though
OL,11,Fthere weren't any issues with their
OL,12,Fhomes.
OL,14,FIrshad Ahmed claims he was hounded by
OL,15,FSSB Law, and told their surveys
OL,16,Frevealed damage caused by faulty
OL,17,Finsulation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
