OL,3,CHomeowners hit with huge fees after
OL,4,Claw firm collapse appeal for
OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,FWhen his case got to court, however,
OL,8,Fhe was told the evidence was
OL,9,Finadequate - and now that SSB Law has
OL,10,Fgone bust, he's been told he has to
OL,11,Fpay #15,000.
OL,13,FHe said: "When I told my wife and
OL,14,Fchildren about this, they blamed me.
OL,15,FThey said you shouldn't have gone with
OL,16,Fthem - and I felt guilty. My wife and
OL,17,Fme, we've been arguing ever since."
OL,19,FLike many others, Irshad says he can't
OL,20,Fpay off his costs - but also can't
OL,21,Fafford to seek further legal advice.
OL,26,@uD@JOUyD@cO]
