OL,3,CHomeowners hit with huge fees after
OL,4,Claw firm collapse appeal for
OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,F"I'm on a pension now struggling to
OL,8,Fpay bills. Where am I going to find
OL,9,F#15,000 to pay them? They keep
OL,10,Fcontacting me, sending me court
OL,11,Forders. I don't know what to do - if
OL,12,Fyou go into a solicitors, they want to
OL,13,Fcharge you #350 an hour so you end up
OL,14,Fin the same boat again."
OL,16,FSSB Law was approached for comment,
OL,17,Fbut since they have gone into
OL,18,Fadministration, no one was able to
OL,19,Frespond.
