OL,5,CGovernment help
OL,7,FFRP, the administrators for SSB Law,
OL,8,Fsaid: "While SSB is no longer trading,
OL,9,Fwe've secured the transition of al
OL,11,Fl live case work to new providers and
OL,12,Fhave notified clients. We'll be
OL,13,Fmanaging that process over the coming
OL,14,Fweeks to ensure a smooth transition."
OL,16,FBut that process has not been smooth -
OL,17,Fand many like Irshad and Ailsa now
OL,18,Fhope that where the law has failed
OL,19,Fthem, Government can step in.
